General.Name: CUE Energy Resources Ltd
General.Description: Cue Energy Resources Limited, an oil and gas exploration and production company, explores for, develops, and produces petroleum. It has petroleum assets in Australia, New Zealand, and Indonesia. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
